description: Variation of Conditions 1, 5 and 6  of planning permission dated 15 July 2016 (RN: 16/05384/FULL) for the: Use of Leicester Square gardens for a pop-up Christmas event over three temporary periods between 11 November 2016 to 8 January 2017, 10 November 2017 to 7 January 2018, and 9 November 2018 to 6 January 2019. Namely, to allow changes to layout including the addition of 6no. stalls in the west terrace and extension of the temporary use (8 November 2019 - 5 January 2020) plus set up and removal dates (23 October 2019 and  13 January 2020).
decision_conditions: Dvpmt in accordance with approvd plans
